      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical work before it is roadworthy. The engine has a persistent knock and requires a top-end rebuild, and the electrical system has several shorts affecting the lighting and dashboard instruments. The body shows visible rust on the rocker panels and the interior upholstery is heavily worn. This is an ideal project car or parts donor for someone with the right tools and expertise.",
